function Start(snoQuest, idActorFollower)
	idFollower = Hydra.QuestGetFollower("QST_Scos_Downs_Artair_Follower")
	
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idFollower) then
		Hydra.ActorPlayConversation(conv_Artair_Search, idSelf, idFollower)
	end
end

function Start(idActor, snoQuest)
	idFollower = Hydra.QuestGetFollower("QST_Scos_Downs_Artair_Follower")
	
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idFollower) then
		Hydra.QuestFollowerTakeOwnership(idFollower)
		Hydra.ActorPlayConversation(conv_Artair_Bark, idSelf, idFollower)
		Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idFollower, id_Artair_Farm, "npc_run", true)
		Hydra.QActorFadeAndDelete(idFollower, 0.5)
	end
end

function Start()
	idFollower = Hydra.QuestGetFollower("QST_Scos_Downs_Artair_Follower")
	
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idFollower) then
		Hydra.ActorPlayConversation(conv_Artair_Recap, idSelf, idFollower)
	end
	
	Hydra.WaitForConversationFinished(conv_Artair_Recap)
	Hydra.EventSend("Start_UnholyBloodlines_Ambush")
end

function Start(idActorNPC, sConversation, idActorPlayer)
	idClone = Hydra.CreatePersonalClone(id_Artair_Farm)
	
	Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idClone, marker_Artair_RunTo, "npc_run", false)
	Hydra.QActorDeletePersonalClone(idClone)
end
